channel.title: Someone please help me get this online
channel.description:
I currently don't have enough in donations so I can not renew my VPS. So meanwhile I want to host it on my new laptop, but I am using utorrent, so I set the port to 43594 and all that jazz. But when I run the server and check canyouseeme.org or runel*cus status check then both say the server should be online.. but no one can login including myself and I am obviously using localhost for myself..
I know the ip is set right and all that..
If anyone can help me get it online I would GREATLY appreciate it and even pay something if wanted..
